metadata.name: Modernist Genesis 2.0 #1
metadata.description: 1 of 9724 uniquely identifiable Modernists Genesis consisting of four randomly selected art and music blocks creating a unique, multidimensional popart experience. It is a ticket and token to activate gameplay in phase 2 through SplitMinting™, which unlocks reward raffles, higher membership tiers, and a pathway to Club MŌDE.
